  <h2>External Resources</h2>

  <p>While this site aims to be comprehensive, these external resources provide additional perspectives:</p>

  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Verlan" target="_blank">Wikipedia: Verlan</a> - General overview with linguistic context</li>
